# Pin <5.0 — transformers 5.x removed `is_tf_available` and other utility
# symbols that the rest of the ecosystem (incl. transformers.pipeline()'s
# own internal imports on certain code paths) still references, surfacing
# as ``ImportError: cannot import name 'is_tf_available' from
# 'transformers.utils'`` on every PII redactor invocation.
# History: PR #447 (5.7→5.8) broke prod 2026-05-07, fixed by 0e01bd2.
# Dependabot then walked the upper bound back up (#556 5.7→5.8, #652
# 5.8→5.9), re-breaking prod 2026-05-21. Hard ceiling at 5.0 + a
# dependabot ignore on minor+major bumps prevents the cycle from
# recurring. Re-evaluate only when the upstream ABI gap is resolved.
